Install by writing

    python setup.py install --user

or, if for all users (might require special privileges):

    python setup.py install

Note that the run-script is might not end up in path if
installing only for user. In such case refer to documentation for
how to add it.

These non-standard modules are required:

    numpy
    scipy
    matplotlib

For building documentation etc, also required

    sphinx
    numpydoc
